AtomicCoordinatesFormat ScaledCartesian
WriteCoorXmol .true.
LatticeConstant 4.3607 Ang
MeshCutoff 150 Ry
MaxSCFIterations 200
DM.NumberPulay  4 
DM.MixingWeight 0.05
DM.Tolerance	0.0004
DM.UseSaveDM .true.
MD.TypeOfRun CG 
MD.NumCGsteps 0

%block kgrid_Monkhorst_Pack
4 	0 	0	0.0
0 	4 	0	0.0
0 	0	4	0.0
%endblock kgrid_Monkhorst_Pack
%block LatticeVectors
-0.5     0.5      0
0       0.5       -0.5
1.0     0.0      1.0
%endblock LatticeVectors
SpinPolarized 	.true.
WriteMullikenPop 1
